## 3. Rule-Based Scoring Mechanism

Each incoming sensor sample is evaluated using the following scoring logic:

| Condition | Score |
|---------|-------|
| Temperature outside normal range | +1 |
| Pulse rate outside normal range | +1 |
| Respiration rate outside normal range | +1 |
| Vibration exceeds threshold | +1 |

---

## 4. Stress Level Assignment Rules

Based on the cumulative score:

| Total Score | Stress Level | Label |
|------------|-------------|------|
| 0 â€“ 1 | 0 | Normal |
| 2 | 1 | Moderate Stress |
| â‰¥ 3 | 2 | High Stress |

These labels are used both for **training** and **validating** the machine learning moDEL
